    content: "Unlike other frameworks that dictate how your site looks, Tailwind provides low-level utility classes that let you build completely custom designs without ever leaving your HTML.",
    icon: 'ðŸŽ¨',
    delay: 200
  },
  {
    title: 'Pixel-Perfect Consistency',
    content: "Every utility class in Tailwind is part of a carefully crafted design system, ensuring your projects maintain consistent spacing, sizing, colors, and more.",
    icon: 'âœ¨',
    delay: 300
  },
  {
    title: 'Optimized for Performance and SEO',
    content: "Tailwind automatically removes all unused CSS when building for production, which means your final CSS bundle is the smallest it could possibly be.",
    icon: 'âš¡',
    delay: 400
  },
  {
